<div>
<p begin="00:00:00.179" end="00:00:08.910" style="s2">So we can&#39;t impose enlightened behavior.<br />It&#39;s an oxymoron. We can help to elicit</p>
<p begin="00:00:08.910" end="00:00:14.250" style="s2">it, help to foster and engender it. And so<br />when we look at the range of human</p>
<p begin="00:00:14.250" end="00:00:20.250" style="s2">behavior from the most creative,<br />self-directed, altruistic, positive kind</p>
<p begin="00:00:20.250" end="00:00:24.630" style="s2">of behavior, to the most violent or<br />impulse or destructive behavior, and then</p>
<p begin="00:00:24.630" end="00:00:30.900" style="s2">we look at what kinds of influences<br />predispose each of those kinds of</p>
<p begin="00:00:30.900" end="00:00:35.670" style="s2">behavior? What kind of world would we<br />need to put in place where stewards of</p>
<p begin="00:00:35.670" end="00:00:40.170" style="s2">the cosmos were the natural emergent<br />byproduct of that system? And how do we</p>
<p begin="00:00:40.170" end="00:00:45.079" style="s2">help bring that about where then it<br />becomes self propagating?</p>
</div>
